description: Community Smiles provides cleanings, diagnostic x-rays, and encourages regular hygiene and maintenance. Also specializes in Pediatric Dental Care, Removable Prosthetics, Crown and Bridge, Endodontics, Periodontics, Orthodontics, Implants, and Oral Surgery. Community Smiles is a nonprofit organization that also hosts a residency program for doctors (Florida Institute for Advanced Dental Education).
name: COMMUNITY SMILES
